pddl.prompt:
Your name is hanoi_solver. You are tasked with modeling the Tower of Hanoi puzzle with 7 disks. You are in an environment with the following public information:
{environment->public_information}
You have the following knowledge:
{agents->hanoi_solver->private_information}
This is the global goal to solve:
{agents->hanoi_solver->goal}
Think step by step and provide a PDDL domain and a PDDL problem file to solve the task. Ensure your PDDL definition allows for the optimal sequence of 127 moves.
Enclose the pddl domain between <domain></domain> tags, and the pddl problem between <problem></problem> tags.
